name: Newcastle to the coast map print
description:
A hand-drawn map print of Newcastle upon Tyne and the surrounding area. Full of crap drawings, musings and mistakes. And a big Byker Grove reference. Sorry Byker residents.

Signed litho print on 300gsm fine art paper from an original ink drawing.

A1 (841 x 594mm)

Frame not included.

£5 from the sale of each print will be given to Choysez, a charity that works with disadvantaged young people throughout Northumberland who need additional support and guidance to help them access a brighter future. Choysez gives them the chance to overcome the problems they face by helping them to gain awards and qualifications as well as aiding their personal development through challenging activities. It seeks to provide our young people with social, employable and essential life skills.
 
Registered charity number 1089811.
